      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical and in-house post-processing scripts under documented version control; regression test suite executed prior to simulation campaign.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1 is a commercially validated solver with documented QA processes. In-house Python post-processing scripts are stored in a Git repository with tagged releases and a regression test suite covering all QoI extraction routines. Achieved level 3 exceeds the required level 2 for this medium model-risk context."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
