      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities performed on the same construct geometry, material system, and loading mode as the COU; at least two independent laboratories contribute data.",
      "rationale": "Validation testing performed on the identical non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct geometry and material system as the COU. Loading mode (ASTM F1717 static compression-bending) is identical to the COU. Two independent laboratories contributed N=11 constructs, providing inter-laboratory reproducibility evidence. Required level 3 achieved."
    }
